01:26:50.939 --> 01:26:53.241
We can't...

01:26:53.241 --> 01:26:55.043
We can't.

01:26:55.043 --> 01:26:57.045
I'm so sorry.

01:26:57.045 --> 01:26:58.846
-[car engine starting] -[gasps]

01:26:58.846 --> 01:27:00.815
