01:27:10.158 --> 01:27:12.994
[♪♪♪]

01:27:20.101 --> 01:27:22.971
[♪♪♪]

01:27:39.687 --> 01:27:42.190
You still got us.

01:27:42.190 --> 01:27:43.891
Yeah.

01:27:44.959 --> 01:27:47.795
